\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/home_walls2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">The System Components - 1,2,3:</span></b>\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Stabilizing Primer</b>\r\n\r\nThis product is a basecoat for use on new or aging building substrates or over existing chalky or friable paint surfaces. This primer is uniquely formulated for optimal penetration and allows for enhanced adhesion of subsequent coats. Primer dries clear but can be pigmented to add hiding power if required.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-183\" alt=\"Walls2\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Walls2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Storm Seal HD</b>\r\n\r\nThis product is a highly elastic and uniquely durable waterproofing formula that will bridge hairline cracks and surface imperfections. It is able to withstand extreme temperature changes and ultraviolet light exposure.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-198\" alt=\"walls_dalton\" src=\"http://buccaneercoatings.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/walls_dalton1.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Wall Seal</b>\r\n\r\nThis product is a flexible, yet hard surface, acrylic topcoat designed to preserve and protect walls. It is ideal for a long-term decorative finish, capable of withstanding the elements.\r\n\r\nThe S-26 Wall Protection System is a 6-in-1 solution for all external wall maintenance issues:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>All Weather Resistant;</li>\r\n	<li>Fully waterproof capable of bridging cracks, joints and surface imperfections, preventing the ingress of water and moisture  into any structure;</li>\r\n	<li>Thermo plastic and will flex with any surface without cracking due to structural movement as well as thermal expansion and contraction;</li>\r\n	<li>Preserves against general degradation;</li>\r\n	<li>Reduces maintenance costs; and</li>\r\n	<li>Decorates and upgrades any building structure.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186\" alt=\"walls\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/walls.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"562\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Concrete and Masonry</b>\r\n\r\nThis product is a solvent-based, fully waterproof floor coating well suited to high-traffic areas such as balconies, walls, garage floors, and parkades. This clear, solvent based product is well suited for protecting brick, natural stone, and cultured stone facing from staining, water ingress and related freeze thaw damage.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" alt=\"walls_concrete\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/walls_concrete.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />','Walls','','publish','closed','closed','','walls','','','2013-02-25 20:36:05','2013-02-26 03:36:05','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=application&#038;p=78',0,'application','',0),(79,1,'2013-01-27 19:44:31','2013-01-28 02:44:31','','Application Fields','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_application-fields','','','2013-01-27 21:31:53','2013-01-28 04:31:53','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=acf&#038;p=79',0,'acf','',0),(80,1,'2013-02-25 20:35:20','2013-02-26 03:35:20','The <b>S-26 Plastic Wall Coating System</b> is based on an uncompromising blend of proprietary resins; it offers the best possible leak and moisture protection for outdoor walls. This system contains a highly durable, pure acrylic binder. Once applied it provides a high strength, waterproof film with excellent elastic properties, resistance to ultraviolet radiation, as well as wide temperature fluctuations.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-182\" alt=\"home_walls\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/home_walls2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\n\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">The System Components - 1,2,3:</span></b>\n\n<b>S-26 Stabilizing Primer</b>\n\nThis product is a basecoat for use on new or aging building substrates or over existing chalky or friable paint surfaces. This primer is uniquely formulated for optimal penetration and allows for enhanced adhesion of subsequent coats. Primer dries clear but can be pigmented to add hiding power if required.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-183\" alt=\"Walls2\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Walls2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\n\n<b>S-26 Storm Seal HD</b>\n\nThis product is a highly elastic and uniquely durable waterproofing formula that will bridge hairline cracks and surface imperfections. It is able to withstand extreme temperature changes and ultraviolet light exposure.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-198\" alt=\"walls_dalton\" src=\"http://buccaneercoatings.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/walls_dalton1.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\n\n<b>S-26 Wall Seal</b>\n\nThis product is a flexible, yet hard surface, acrylic topcoat designed to preserve and protect walls. It is ideal for a long-term decorative finish, capable of withstanding the elements.\n\nThe S-26 Wall Protection System is a 6-in-1 solution for all external wall maintenance issues:\n<ol>\n	<li>All Weather Resistant;</li>\n	<li>Fully waterproof capable of bridging cracks, joints and surface imperfections, preventing the ingress of water and moisture  into any structure;</li>\n	<li>Thermo plastic and will flex with any surface without cracking due to structural movement as well as thermal expansion and contraction;</li>\n	<li>Preserves against general degradation;</li>\n	<li>Reduces maintenance costs; and</li>\n	<li>Decorates and upgrades any building structure.</li>\n</ol>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186\" alt=\"walls\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/walls.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"562\" />\n\n<b>S-26 Concrete and Masonry</b>\n\nThis product is a solvent-based, fully waterproof floor coating well suited to high-traffic areas such as balconies, walls, garage floors, and parkades. This clear, solvent based product is well suited for protecting brick, natural stone, and cultured stone facing from staining, water ingress and related freeze thaw damage.Once applied, it creates a seamless floor casing resistant to UV damage, freeze/thaw conditions and a variety of chemicals and lubricants.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" alt=\"walls_concrete\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/walls_concrete.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />','Walls','','inherit','open','open','','78-autosave','','','2013-02-25 20:35:20','2013-02-26 03:35:20','',78,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/2013/01/27/78-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(81,1,'2013-01-27 20:20:37','2013-01-28 03:20:37','Buccaneer offers a cold process roofing system suitable for a wide cross-section of roofing substrates from flat to fully pitched roofs.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-187\" alt=\"home_roofing\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/home_roofing2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Sloped Roofing</span></b>\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Storm Seal LD</b>\r\n\r\nThis liquid plastic is a distinctive cold process roofing product that is able to stretch and flex with a wide cross-section of sloped roof substrates through extreme temperature changes. This product’s lightfast pigments will retain colour and protect its substrate against the harshest of elements including: ultraviolet light, snow, rain, and chemical pollution. It can be applied to any existing tile, metal, wood, fiberglass, or asbestos roof.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-188\" alt=\"roofing\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/roofing.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Flat Roofing</span></b>\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Storm Seal HD</b>\r\n\r\nThis product is an integral component of Buccaneer’s cold process roofing system. It works by forming a thick plastic skin that will remain flexible and durable while waterproofing virtually any roofing substrate including: concrete, concrete tiles, steel, wood, and asbestos.\r\n\r\nWhile developing S-26 Storm Seal HD, Buccaneer focused on the foundation of the product - a Waterproof material capable of adhering to a wide cross section of substrate, with sufficient strength to bridge hairline cracks and flexibility to accommodate expansion and contraction.\r\n\r\nOur proprietary resin and high quality pigments work to preserve this unique blend of characteristics over extended periods of exposure to the harshest ultraviolet light, environmental conditions.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-184\" alt=\"wall_stormseal\" src=\"http://buccaneercoatings.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/wall_stormseal.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Storm Seal VHD</b>\r\n\r\nA derivative of S-26 Storm Seal HD, this product incorporates plastic fibers into the mastic thereby increasing its tensile strength. Well suited for seams, joints, and transition areas were high stress torsional forces may concentrate.\r\n\r\n<b>Base Coats</b>\r\n\r\nWhere required, Buccaneer draws on a selection of base coats to suite a full spectrum of roofing substrates.\r\n\r\n<b>Polyester Fabrics</b>\r\n\r\nUtilized in particularly demanding applications where extra waterproofing measures are warranted. Such surfaces include steel roof seams, joints and roof/wall transitions. Our cold seal roofing process can incorporate the use of polyester fabrics between consecutive coats of Storm Seal.\r\n\r\n<i>This product is 100% environmentally friendly, is water soluble, and contains ultra-low levels of V.O.C.’s.</i>','Roofing','','publish','closed','closed','','roofing','','','2013-02-25 20:37:07','2013-02-26 03:37:07','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=application&#038;p=81',0,'application','',0),(82,1,'2013-01-27 20:21:17','2013-01-28 03:21:17','Wood is a unique surface because it is a natural material that expands, contracts, absorbs water, and warps long after it has been hewn from a tree. Wood products are vulnerable to sunlight, insect infestation, moisture and general age degradation. Therefore, it is important for any wood preservation product to not only protect against this damage but also be able to move and flex continuously with the wood. Buccaneer’s range of wood preservation products are a unique blend of water-soluble plastic polymers that are durable and have a simple application process. They can be used on new or existing wooden structures.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-189\" alt=\"home_wood\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/home_wood2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative</b>\r\n\r\nThis water borne, ultra-low VOC product is unlike any other available wood coating. It is designed for all vertical external woodwork including: garage doors, fencing, window frames, and timber homes. S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative works by forming a water resistant, mould and mildew proof barrier that is resistant to ultraviolet degradation. Once this product is applied, it maintains a flexible surface capable of expanding and contracting with the wood in order to prevent cracking during extreme temperature changes.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-190\" alt=\"wood2\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/wood2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"562\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Wooden Deck Coating </b>\r\n\r\nThis product is a derivative of the S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative. S-26 Wooden Deck Coating is a non-slip formula that ensures secure footing even in damp conditions. It was specially formulated to withstand the added rigors of foot traffic and ultra-high ultraviolet exposure.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191\" alt=\"wood_coating\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/wood_coating.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"560\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Clear Seal-Wood</b>\r\n\r\nS-26 Clear Seal -Wood is a solvent borne, fully waterproof, clear topcoat utilized to complement S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative in high impact applications such as: outdoor furniture, railings, stair treds and decks. This product is an easy to use, single pack, quick drying formula.','Wood','','publish','closed','closed','','wood','','','2013-02-16 09:00:27','2013-02-16 16:00:27','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=application&#038;p=82',0,'application','',0),(83,1,'2013-01-27 20:22:20','2013-01-28 03:22:20','Wood is a unique surface because it is a natural material that expands, contracts, absorbs water, and warps long after it has been hewn from a tree. Wood products are vulnerable to sunlight, insect infestation, moisture and general age degradation. Therefore, it is important for any wood preservation product to not only protect against this damage but also be able to move and flex continuously with the wood. Buccaneer’s range of wood preservation products are a unique blend of water-soluble plastic polymers that are durable and have a simple application process. They can be used on new or existing wooden structures.\n\n<b>S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative</b>\n\nThis water borne, ultra-low VOC product is unlike any other available wood coating. It is designed for all vertical external woodwork including: garage doors, fencing, window frames, and timber homes. S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative works by forming a water resistant, mould and mildew proof barrier that is resistant to ultraviolet degradation. Once this product is applied, it maintains a flexible surface capable of expanding and contracting with the wood in order to prevent cracking during extreme temperature changes.\n\n<b>S-26 Wooden Deck Coating </b>\n\nThis product is a derivative of the S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative. S-26 Wooden Deck Coating is a non-slip formula that ensures secure footing even in damp conditions. It was specially formulated to withstand the added rigors of foot traffic and ultra-high ultraviolet exposure.\n\n<b>S-26 Clear Seal-Wood</b>\n\nS-26 Clear Seal -Wood is a solvent borne, fully waterproof, clear topcoat utilized to complement S-26 Plastic Wood Preservative in high impact applications such as: outdoor furniture, railings, stair treds and decks. This product is an easy to use, single pack, quick drying formula.','','','inherit','open','open','','82-autosave','','','2013-01-27 20:22:20','2013-01-28 03:22:20','',82,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/2013/01/27/82-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(85,1,'2013-01-27 20:25:06','2013-01-28 03:25:06','From face brick to driveways, the S-26 flooring series prevents damage caused by moisture and is resistant to alkalis, ultraviolet light and staining. Each product in this series offers protection against the elements.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-192\" alt=\"home_floor\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/home_floor2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"562\" />\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Face Brick, Stone and Floor Sealers</span></b><b>                       </b>\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Clear Seal - Concrete and Masonry</b>\r\n\r\nThis clear, solvent based product is a penetrating sealant that provides a highly durable, non-yellowing protective film for brick, stonework, terrazzo concrete and existing epoxy finishes.  It prevents damage typically caused by moisture and UV degradation and wear and tear by bonding to the surface and creating a hard wearing, waterproof barrier. S-26 Clear Seal is resistant to alkalis, ultraviolet light and staining. This is one of the most versatile, long-lasting clear plastic coatings ever developed.\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Plastic Floor Coating</b>\r\n\r\nThis pigmented, solvent based, floor coating protects concrete floors, balconies and exterior walkways against wear and tear caused by moisture ingress, ultraviolet radiation and extreme weather conditions. It is extremely tough, hardwearing and waterproof.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-193\" alt=\"floor_plastic\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/floor_plastic.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<i>This product is offered in a variety of colours and comes in a non-slip version. </i>\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Epoxy Floor Enamel</b>\r\n\r\nThis twin pack, pigmented, plastic floor enamel is ideal for high traffic areas prone to exposure to solvents, lubricants and other potentially corrosive fluids. It is a heavy-duty seamless floor cladding that is resistant to many harsh solvents and chemicals.  Apply this enamel to floors and walls in shops or processing areas to create a seamless, sealed coating between floor and wall.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-194\" alt=\"floor_enamel\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/floor_enamel.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\r\n\r\n<b>S-26 Water Based Floor Coating</b>\r\n\r\nThis single pack, pigmented, plastic product has a highly durable, non-slip finish ideally suited for use in areas such as stairwells, mechanical rooms, storage areas and other confined spaces where fume buildup may pose a fire or inhalation hazard. Also, Ulta-low volatile organic compound (VOC) makes for odorless application.','Floors & Driveways','','publish','closed','closed','','floors-driveways','','','2013-02-25 20:39:33','2013-02-26 03:39:33','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=application&#038;p=85',0,'application','',0),(86,1,'2013-01-27 20:25:27','2013-01-28 03:25:27','<b>S-26 Concrete and Masonry</b>\r\n\r\nThis product is a solvent-based, fully waterproof floor coating well suited to high-traffic areas such as balconies, <a title=\"Walls\" href=\"/walls\">walls</a>, garage floors, and parkades. Once applied, it creates a seamless floor casing resistant to UV damage, freeze/thaw conditions and a variety of chemicals and lubricants.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-195\" alt=\"Decks\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Decks.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />','Decks & Balconies','','publish','closed','closed','','decks-balconies','','','2013-02-16 09:03:12','2013-02-16 16:03:12','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=application&#038;p=86',0,'application','',0),(87,1,'2013-02-25 20:41:03','2013-02-26 03:41:03','<b>S-26 Concrete and Masonry</b>\n\nThis product is a solvent-based, fully waterproof floor coating well suited to high-traffic areas such as balconies, <a title=\"Walls\" href=\"/walls\">walls</a>, garage floors, and parkades. Once applied, it creates a seamless floor casing resistant to UV damage, freeze/thaw conditions and a variety of chemicals and lubricants.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-195\" alt=\"Decks\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Decks.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />','Decks & Balconies','','inherit','open','open','','86-autosave','','','2013-02-25 20:41:03','2013-02-26 03:41:03','',86,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/2013/01/27/86-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(88,1,'2013-01-27 20:29:48','2013-01-28 03:29:48','<b>S-26 Plastic Crack Filler</b>\r\n\r\nThis product can be used in any type of crack or void to repair damage in minutes.  This water soluble formulation is environmentally friendly. Unlike powdered crack fillers, the S-26 Plastic Crack Filler is flexible, waterproof and will move with a structure’s substrata to prevent future cracking. Where extra hardness is desired, incorporate Portland cement into the crack filler prior to application.  Crack filler can be used with cement, concrete, plasterwork and woodwork, making it one of the most versatile fillers in the world.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-144\" alt=\"home_cracks\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/home_cracks1.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />','Cracks','','publish','closed','closed','','cracks','','','2013-02-16 09:04:05','2013-02-16 16:04:05','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?post_type=application&#038;p=88',0,'application','',0),(89,1,'2013-01-05 21:47:49','2013-01-06 04:47:49','Based in Calgary, Alberta, Buccaneer Canada is a manufacturer and distributor of <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">liquid plastic coating</span> <i>(link to internal page on liquid applied protection)</i> systems designed to preserve and protect a wide spectrum of building materials and surfaces. Learn more about our <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">applications</span>.\r\n\r\nBuccaneer coating solutions have a 35-year history of development and application in the United Kingdom and South Africa. Over the years applications have spread throughout South Africa, the Benelux Countries, Iceland and Canada.\r\n\r\nAt Buccaneer, our mission is to produce the highest quality coatings utilizing our proprietary formulations with uncompromising raw material inputs. Combing ease of use and superior durability provides a cost effective and long term coating solution for our customers while respecting the environment by using only eco-friendly acceptable raw materials that are not hazardous to people, animals or the environment.','About','','inherit','open','open','','38-revision-2','','','2013-01-05 21:47:49','2013-01-06 04:47:49','',38,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/2013/01/05/38-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(90,1,'2013-01-27 20:33:25','2013-01-28 03:33:25','<h2>Architectural and Industrial Coating Systems</h2>\r\nOne of the first questions we typically get at Buccaneer is “why plastic, why not paint?”. Our plastic architectural and industrial coating systems have proved themselves as far more durable than conventional paints and varnishes.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-179\" alt=\"Coating_systems\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/Coating_systems.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"560\" />\r\n\r\nPlastics do not degrade over time or become a hazard. Instead, they protect and preserve the <a title=\"Applications\" href=\"/applications\">surfaces</a> to which they are applied.\r\n\r\nExtensive research and development has led to the advancement of proprietary resins and entirely unique formulations. Buccaneer Architectural and Industrial Coating Systems can be applied to all types of <a title=\"Applications\" href=\"/applications\">surfaces</a> including steel, wood, concrete and plaster. The unique chemical formula of this product line allows for maximum durability that will outperform virtually all conventional paint products and give any building or structure a far superior life span dramatically reducing expensive maintenance costs.\r\n\r\nBuccaneer offers both water-borne and solvent-borne protective coating solutions based on the <a title=\"Applications\" href=\"/applications\">application</a> required.','Coating Systems','','publish','open','open','','coating-systems','','','2013-02-16 08:49:26','2013-02-16 15:49:26','',0,'http://buccaneercoatings.com/?page_id=90',0,'page','',0),(91,1,'2013-01-27 20:33:24','2013-01-28 03:33:24','<b>Architectural and Industrial Coating Systems</b>\n\nOne of the first questions we typically get at Buccaneer is “why plastic, why not paint?”. Our plastic architectural and industrial coating systems have proved themselves as far more durable than conventional paints and varnishes.\n\nPlastics do not degrade over time or become a hazard. Instead, they protect and preserve the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">surfaces</span> <i>(link to applications)</i> to which they are applied.\n\nExtensive research and development has led to the advancement of proprietary resins and entirely unique formulations. Bucca