nd distributor of liquid plastic coating systems designed to preserve and protect a wide spectrum of building materials and surfaces.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button\" href=\"/about\">Learn More »</a>\r\n\r\n</section><section>\r\n<h2>Get In Touch</h2>\r\n<strong>Main Office:</strong>\r\n3621B 3rd Street NE\r\nCalgary, AB Canada\r\nT2E 5V1\r\n\r\n<strong>Phone number:</strong> +1 (403) 452 7005\r\n\r\n<strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@buccaneerprotectivecoatings.com\">info@buccaneerprotectivecoatings.com</a>\r\n\r\n</section>','Home Page','','inherit','open','open','','20-revision-9','','','2013-02-14 00:25:46','2013-02-14 07:25:46','',20,'http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/20-revision-9/',0,'revision','',0),(172,1,'2013-02-16 09:02:09','2013-02-16 16:02:09','From face brick to driveways, the S-26 flooring series prevents damage caused by moisture and is resistant to alkalis, ultraviolet light and staining. Each product in this series offers protection against the elements.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-192\" alt=\"home_floor\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/home_floor2.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"562\" />\n\n<b><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Face Brick, Stone and Floor Sealers</span></b><b>                       </b>\n\n<b>S-26 Clear Seal - Concrete and Masonry</b>\n\nThis solvent based product is a penetrating sealant that provides a highly durable, non-yellowing protective film for brick, stonework, terrazzo concrete and existing epoxy finishes.  It prevents damage typically caused by moisture and UV degradation and wear and tear by bonding to the surface and creating a hard wearing, waterproof barrier. S-26 Clear Seal is resistant to alkalis, ultraviolet light and staining. This is one of the most versatile, long-lasting clear plastic coatings ever developed.\n\n<b>S-26 Plastic Floor Coating</b>\n\nThis solvent based, single pack, pigmented, plastic floor enamel protects concrete floors, balconies and exterior walkways against wear and tear caused by moisture ingress, ultraviolet radiation and extreme weather conditions. It is extremely tough, hardwearing and waterproof.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-193\" alt=\"floor_plastic\" src=\"http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/floor_plastic.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"563\" />\n\n<i>This product is offered in a variety of colours and comes in a non-slip version. </i>\n\n<b>S-26 Epoxy Floor Enamel</b>\n\nThis twin pack, pigmented, plastic floor enamel is ideal for high traffic areas prone to exposure to solvents, lubricants and other potentially corrosive fluids. It is a heavy-duty seamless floor cladding that is resistant to many harsh solvents and chemicals.  Apply this enamel to floors and walls in shops or processing areas to create a seamless, sealed coating between floor and wall.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>S-26 Water Based Floor Coating</b>\n\nThis single pack, pigmented, plastic product has a highly durable, non-slip finish ideally suited for use in areas such as stairwells, mechanical rooms, storage areas and other confined spaces where fume buildup may pose a fire or inhalation hazard. Also, Ulta-low volatile organic compound (VOC) makes for odorless application.','Floors & Driveways','','inherit','open','open','','85-autosave','','','2013-02-16 09:02:09','2013-02-16 16:02:09','',85,'http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/85-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(174,1,'2013-02-14 00:26:21','2013-02-14 07:26:21','Based in Calgary, Alberta, Buccaneer Canada is a manufacturer and distributor of <a title=\"Coating Systems\" href=\"/coating-systems/\">Architectural and Industrial Coating Systems</a> designed to preserve and protect a wide spectrum of building materials and surfaces. Learn more about our <a title=\"Applications\" href=\"/applications/\">applications</a>.\r\n\r\nBuccaneer coating solutions have a 35-year history of development and application in the United Kingdom and South Africa. Over the years applications have spread throughout South Africa, the Benelux Countries, Iceland, and Canada.\r\n\r\nAt Buccaneer, our mission is to produce the highest quality coatings utilizing our proprietary formulations with uncompromising raw material inputs. Combining ease of use and superior durability provides a cost effective and long term coating solution for our customers while respecting the environment by using only eco-friendly acceptable raw materials that are not hazardous to people, animals or the environment.','About','','inherit','open','open','','38-revision-6','','','2013-02-14 00:26:21','2013-02-14 07:26:21','',38,'http://buccaneer.spiraldesign.ca/38-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(175,1,'2013-02-14 00:18:40','2013-02-14 07:18:40','<h2>Architectural and Industrial Coating Systems</h2>\r\n\r\nOne of the first questions we typically get at Buccaneer is “why plastic, why not paint?”. Our plastic architectural and industrial coating systems have proved themselves as far more durable than conventional paints and varnishes.\r\n\r\nPlastics do not degrade over time or become a hazard. Instead, they protect and preserve the <a title=\"Applications\" href=\"/applications\">surfaces</a> to which they are applied.\r\n\r\nExtensive research and development has led to the advancement of proprietary resins and entirely unique formulations. Buccaneer Architectural and Industrial Coating Systems can be applied to all types of <a title=\"Applications\" href=\"/applications\">surfaces</a> including steel, wood, concrete and plaster. The unique chemical formula of this product line allows for maximum durability that will outperform virtually all conventional paint products and give any building or structure a far superior life span dramatically reducing expensive maintenance costs.\r\n\r\nBuccaneer offers both water-borne and solvent-borne protective coating solutions based on the <a title=\"Applications\" href=\"/applications\">application</a> required.','C